set_light
Disk World creator help
set_light

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_light -  This sets the current light level.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_light(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - The new light level.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/light.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets the current light level.   This method calls adjust_light() 
with the correct value to set the light level.

